snippet.title: Subway Midnight Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
SUBWAY MIDNIGHT!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1750570/Subway_Midnight/?beta=0

A haunted-house style horror game set on a spooky train! 

-Run away from a weirdo!
-Hang out with ghosts!
-Try not to become a ghost yourself!

I solo-dev'd this game for 3 years and it's done! I just need a publisher to help release it!

 If you're a publisher, a journalist, or just generally have any inquiries, you can email me at: BubbyDarkstar@gmail.com or DM me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/bubbydarkstar

Wonderful trailer music done by: https://twitter.com/laryssaokada
